{"tid":1489501,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"認為討論 做個安份守己既情人真係咁難？","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:48:16.000Z","uid":64509,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"640be1c9ce16e391195567197e04d284bccbb41a","tid":1489501,"uid":64509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"有幾多人可以滿足現況<br />\n真係為左面前依棵樹放棄整片森林？<br />\n當初開始左個刻 唔係應該要學識無拖實唔放咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">專一唔係愛情基本要求咩？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說 <span style=\"color: gold;\">我人生已經第三次比有女朋友既男仔溝</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 次次都係事後先知<br />\n次次身邊人話個真相比我聽之後<br />\n真係頭都大埋 知道後會即刻斷絕來往 因為佢今日為得我同眼前人分手  <span style=\"color: gold;\">他朝一日個個受害者都可以係我</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋 上個ex都係因為唔安份守己 周圍flirt下周邊女女 初初話係好傾啲朋友 但其實係一直睇下邊個條件好啲 啱feel啲 得米成事就隨時走 所以次次拍拖都無痕接軌 所以我唔會成為其中一個咁既女仔<br />\n<br />\n不過知道原來佢有女朋友都hurt... 因為都傾左一段日子了 幾啱feel 唉 做人真係唔好太有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">做人定做狗 趁你仲有得揀 好揀<br />\n我都係提醒下自己<br />\n咩事都好 守住良知。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d6cd5bc2eba26b634f1206d9a7ea32158f491958","tid":1489501,"uid":64509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb87c5ebcb08d1afa914c3f727d3ac9f26dec52","tid":1489501,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"圖都無張好難討論落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151062fb4f195669047a840cbb2efa41d4298661","tid":1489501,"uid":64509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"*認真討論"},{"pid":"fda03b29ea06548941273e4ded3a4bd38e6b3648","tid":1489501,"uid":210182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"係真 呢個時候你唔斷絕來往就後患無窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他朝一日個受害者會係自己係真 <br />\n樓主記得一定要企硬 報應依家野遲早到返自己到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92d2d912b61f87c404fe278ef1ce33caa137605","tid":1489501,"uid":306631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"現實係安分守己嘅巴打冇絲會睇得上orz"},{"pid":"bbbb4be6fa7300a9dba853cb145c9b5936a7e68b","tid":1489501,"uid":210182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:11:41.000Z","msg":"不過如果最後真係一齊左<br />\n希望樓主你都唔好成日形住對方會再出軌<br />\n如果唔係自己就會好辛苦<br />\n當然最好當然係等個男既搞清楚先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed454d3e6123b79fc634b43d885ebb83f8d82382","tid":1489501,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"我係"},{"pid":"6927786a45e6c198060edb70367e92f0573414f8","tid":1489501,"uid":46457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"其實你都要諗下自己係咪有D咩特質，特別吸引呢種人<br />\n<br />\n唔好比人覺得你咁易得手囉"},{"pid":"76b6b6606ccbdc8e85a0b1a7ea54c7a0de13b170","tid":1489501,"uid":64509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed454d3e6123b79fc634b43d885ebb83f8d82382","tid":1489501,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"我係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"係咩？"},{"pid":"900a4eb66a1270062d3d41eb1b37df5a32eb5f15","tid":1489501,"uid":158998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"依家啲人愛情觀錯曬"},{"pid":"51ab6096559fde3601ca1f137a9c2e9f05470d88","tid":1489501,"uid":100909,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"我以前拍拖都係你所講既無痕接軌 甚至拍拖期間出軌幾次 啲ex忍我等我我都唔識珍惜<br />\n但直至遇到而家個男朋友（都係無痕接軌咁同佢一齊） 我成個人變左 變到好專一真係對佢一心一意 第一次覺得為愛既人付出 見到佢開心其實